text: O'Reilly Auto Parts is an American auto parts retailer. provides automotive aftermarket parts, tools, supplies, equipment, and accessories to professional service providers and do-it-yourself customers. It is headquartered in Springfield, Missouri. It was founded in 1957. It has 6,000 stores in 48 states, Puerto Rico, and Mexico.
